[1mDESCRIPTION[0m
       [1mGlobash  [22mis  a  special shell for Global using GNU bash.  You can use a
       lot of functions to ease reading source code, like tag stack, tag  mark
       and cookie.  At first, you should make tag files using [1mgtags [22mand invoke
       this  command  in  the  project.   Please  refer  to  the  help   (type
       'ghelp<RET>') for detailed usage.

